<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 12:27:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>印度外长苏杰生将访问巴基斯坦出席上海合作组织峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-foreign-minister-jaishankar-visit-pakistan-sco-summit-2024-10-04/</link><description>印度外交部发言人周五表示，印度外长苏杰生将于本月访问巴基斯坦参加上海合作组织（SCO）峰会。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 12:02:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-foreign-minister-jaishankar-visit-pakistan-sco-summit-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟就中国电动汽车关税进行投票后，斯特兰蒂斯表示稳定的规则“比以往任何时候都更加重要”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-after-eu-vote-china-ev-tariffs-says-stable-rules-more-important-than-2024-10-04/</link><description>Stellantis周五表示，在欧盟成员国投票支持对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税后，该公司支持自由公平的竞争、稳定的规则和支持需求的政策。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 11:13:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-after-eu-vote-china-ev-tariffs-says-stable-rules-more-important-than-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，中国敦促欧盟推迟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-eu-delay-implementing-tariffs-china-made-evs-state-media-says-2024-10-04/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国周五呼吁欧盟推迟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税，避免贸易摩擦升级。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:56:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-eu-delay-implementing-tariffs-china-made-evs-state-media-says-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾指责中国在南海袭击越南渔民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-accuses-china-assaulting-vietnamese-fishermen-south-china-sea-2024-10-04/</link><description>菲律宾周五指责中国海事官员在南中国海有争议的海域对越南渔民进行“无理攻击”，为这场紧张的对抗争端增添了色彩。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:55:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-accuses-china-assaulting-vietnamese-fishermen-south-china-sea-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国快递公司BingEx在美国IPO估值近12亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-courier-firm-bingex-valued-nearly-12-bln-us-ipo-2024-10-04/</link><description>中国BingEx周五表示，其在美国首次公开募股中筹集了6600万美元，这家快递公司的估值为11.7亿美元，这表明投资者风险偏好有所复苏，监管障碍有所缓解。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:46:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-courier-firm-bingex-valued-nearly-12-bln-us-ipo-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟投票支持对中国制造的电动汽车进口征收高额关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-votes-favour-hefty-tariffs-china-made-ev-imports-2024-10-04/</link><description>周五，欧盟支持对中国进口电动汽车（EV）征收高达 45% 的关税，以对抗中国政府对目前针对欧洲的汽车制造商的补贴。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:43:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-votes-favour-hefty-tariffs-china-made-ev-imports-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>德国汽车制造商警告称，欧盟对中国电动汽车关税投票是该行业的“致命信号”，敦促妥协</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/fatal-signal-german-car-industry-slams-eu-china-tariffs-calls-deal-2024-10-04/</link><description>德国顶级汽车制造商周五敦促布鲁塞尔和北京通过谈判达成协议，避免对中国制造的电动汽车进口征收迫在眉睫的关税，凸显了人们对不断升级的贸易冲突对企业意味着什么的担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:18:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/fatal-signal-german-car-industry-slams-eu-china-tariffs-calls-deal-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，德国政府投票反对欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-government-voted-against-eu-tariffs-evs-china-source-says-2024-10-04/</link><description>一位欧盟消息人士周五告诉路透社，德国政府投票反对对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:12:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-government-voted-against-eu-tariffs-evs-china-source-says-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：随着港口罢工结束，就业和石油占主导地位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-04/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:05:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>Alphabet 旗下 Waymo 将利用现代电动汽车扩大机器人出租车车队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/alphabets-waymo-expand-robotaxi-fleet-with-hyundai-evs-2024-10-04/</link><description>两家公司周五表示，随着 Waymo 在美国的扩张，Alphabet 旗下的 Waymo 将在其机器人出租车车队中添加韩国现代汽车的电动汽车。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:02:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/alphabets-waymo-expand-robotaxi-fleet-with-hyundai-evs-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟表示中国电动汽车关税计划获得了成员国的必要支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-says-plans-chinese-ev-tariffs-obtained-necessary-support-member-states-2024-10-04/</link><description>欧盟委员会在一份声明中表示，欧盟委员会对中国制造的电动汽车征收明确关税的提议已获得成员国的必要支持。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 09:27:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-says-plans-chinese-ev-tariffs-obtained-necessary-support-member-states-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>专注于中国的对冲基金九月回报爆炸性增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-focused-hedge-funds-post-explosive-september-returns-2024-10-04/</link><description>由于中国政府激进的经济刺激计划推动中国股市大幅反弹，一些专注于中国的对冲基金在 9 月份报告了爆炸性回报。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 09:20:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-focused-hedge-funds-post-explosive-september-returns-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟消息人士称，欧盟对中国电动汽车关税的投票尚无结果，将由欧盟委员会做出决定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-vote-chinese-ev-tariffs-inconclusive-leaving-eu-commission-decide-eu-sources-2024-10-04/</link><description>欧盟消息人士周五表示，欧盟国家未能明确投票赞成或反对对中国电动汽车征收高达 45% 的关税，让欧盟委员会来决定该怎么做。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 09:09:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-vote-chinese-ev-tariffs-inconclusive-leaving-eu-commission-decide-eu-sources-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟各国政府如何就中国电动汽车关税进行投票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-eu-governments-plan-vote-chinese-ev-tariffs-2024-10-04/</link><description>欧盟委员会周五表示，在欧盟成员国投票中获得了足够的支持，将对中国制造的电动汽车进口征收高达45%的关税。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 08:38:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-eu-governments-plan-vote-chinese-ev-tariffs-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲黄金庆祝活动引发印度和中国假期需求小幅增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-festivities-spark-slight-demand-india-china-holiday-2024-10-04/</link><description>由于即将到来的节日，印度的黄金需求本周略有改善，但由于价格创历史新高，黄金需求仍低于平时，而中国市场因假期休市。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 08:20:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-festivities-spark-slight-demand-india-china-holiday-2024-10-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>